New confirmed cases and new cured cases in Wuhan crossed the "Golden Cross" point today. Since then, the whole country including Wuhan will gradually increase the release of hospital beds as the core of medical resources. However, it should be noted that two anomalies appeared in the data on February 20: One is the huge rebound of new cases in non-hubei areas; and the other is the difference of 220 cases between the "cumulative confirmed cases in Hubei" issued by the National Health and Health Commission and the Hubei Health and Health Commission

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
By Xu Jin, data researcher, Caijing

Image | CAIJING visual center

Editor | Sheryl Rong

1. Cumulative confirmed cases

As of 24:00 on February 20,74,576 cases of new coronary pneumonia had been confirmed in China. The following is a regional trend map.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 1

The trend line of non-hubei area in China is flat, the cumulative cases will not exceed 12700 cases.

2. NEW CASES: Wuhan continues to drop precipitously, while the trend outside Wuhan remains positive

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 2

There were two anomalies in the February 20th data. First, there is a huge rebound in the number of new cases in non-hubei areas. Second, there is a difference of 220 cases between the "cumulative confirmed cases in Hubei" published by the National Health and Health Commission and the Hubei Health and Health Commission.

The first exception takes into account the fact that the prison figures in Shandong and Zhejiang have been released and the relevant leaders (including the director of the Shandong Department of Justice) have been punished at the same time. It can be seen that the illness occurred before and the data were released after, therefore, 227 cases should be excluded from the new addition of the day. There were 31 new cases in non-hubei area on the same day after exclusion, and the trend was unchanged, which was basically consistent with the provincial data.

The second exception is the central government data contradiction, still waiting for official authority to explain or further data adjustment. No speculation (when the Hubei Health Commission corrected 220 additional prison cases, we temporarily "statistical caliber adjustment" processing) .

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 3

February 20 in Wuhan, Hubei Province, confirmed cases batch reduction completed, the new cases from the abnormal decline returned to the normal rate of decline, officially reduced to double-digit levels. It's consistent with what we thought.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 4

The number of new cases in Wuhan dropped sharply again to 319, which could be regarded as the result of the successful completion of the "five hundred percent" campaign in Wuhan. Five "one hundred percent" campaigns in Wuhan are confirmed to be completed. According to the following data, the war situation in Wuhan has been completely reversed.

3. GROWTH RATE OF CONFIRMED CASES: Wuhan has finally dropped below 1% 

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 5

The growth rate of non-hubei region in China dropped to 0.25% and that of Wuhan region in Hubei dropped to 0.54% . Wuhan's growth rate drops sharply to less than 1% .

Close contact tracing: Recent data show a significant increase in tracking efforts in Hubei, which is worth looking forward to

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 6

The non-hubei part of the country has finally stopped and waited. Hubei this index continued to climb for days to catch up, if only look at the recent three-day increment, tracking ratio has reached more than 10.

Both the Party secretary of Hubei Province and the Party Secretary of Wuhan City have recently mentioned the importance of epidemiological investigations. This data can support.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 7

Hubei is still receiving medical observation of the stock of data continues to decline, indicating that the epidemic has slowed. The country's non-hubei region continues to decline significantly, meaning more resources could be released to track new close contacts, if needed.

5. Suspected Cases: fewer new cases, fewer stocks

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 8

Hubei (including Wuhan) new suspected cases rose nearly 400 cases compared with yesterday, should be Wuhan "5% " results.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 9

Hubei recovery of suspected case stocks May reflect 100 percent isolation of suspected cases in Wuhan.

6. Number of hospitalizations: Non Hubei Areas Continue to decline

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
10

It is estimated that there are statistical caliber adjustment factors in Hubei.

The case fatality rate has recovered, but the cure rate has increased at a faster rate

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Figure 11

The case fatality rate continued to rise, due to factors such as the timing of the death and the increase in new diagnoses, as well as the ability to treat and the availability of medical resources. The case fatality rate in Wuhan is still significantly higher than that in Hubei and the whole country.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
12

The cure rate is rising even faster.

Wuhan has crossed the "Golden Cross" point in one fell swoop, the whole situation has reversed. This will be the landmark event of February 20th. Since then, the country including Wuhan will gradually increase the release of hospital beds as the core of medical resources. The battle changed from defense to full-scale attack. It's a celebration!

Summary: Wuhan in the "five hundred percent" decisive battle after success, took a step across the "golden cross point" this decisive step. Marked the Wuhan epidemic and Hubei, like the rest of the country, finally entered the stage of a comprehensive counter-offensive. The speed of resuming work and production outside Hubei is expected to be quickened.
